_field_real.name: hdao ambient shadow#how much ssao shadowing darkens the ambient lighting
hdao point shadow#how much ssao shadowing darkens the point lighting ie the sun
sharp ambient shadow#how much the sharp dynamic shadows darken ambient lighting
sharp point shadow#how much the sharp dynamic shadows darken the point lighting ie the sun
max intensity:[0-1]#unshadowed areas will have this relative intensity
min intensity:[0-1]#fully shadowed areas will have this relative intensity
falloff width#controls the shape of the shadow falloff curve
corner scale#controls shadow sensitivity to corners
corner bias#offsets corner sensitivity, generally to ignore shallow corners
bounds scale#controls the maximum shadow distance, as a ratio of the distance to the object
bounds offset#offsets the maximum shadow distance, generally to make a region of full darkness before fading
near clip:world units#completely removes ssao on anything closer than this
near fade width:world units#distance over which the ssao fades in
far clip:world units#completely removes ssao on anything farther than this
far fade width:world units#distance over which the ssao fades in
